{"tid":1057001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李嘉誠基金會捐1,000萬予養和醫院","createTime":"2019-03-11T14:48:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-11T22:29:40.000Z","uid":28765,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"5d9d652b7c35ae5c089a3f99c907849ab7d0240f","tid":1057001,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:48:04.000Z","msg":"李嘉誠基金會宣佈，捐款1,000萬予養和醫院心臟科中心，推行為期三年的「心臟導管介入資助計劃」，協助有需要病人進行冠狀動脈支架植入術、經導管主動脈心瓣置換術、二或三尖瓣夾合術及左心耳封堵手術等程序。<br />\n養和醫院發言人指，每位病人的資助金額由18至50萬元不等，預計三年會有逾30名病人受惠。除李嘉誠基金會資助手術相關費用外，養和醫院及參與計劃的醫生減收部分住院費及醫生費，病人需要負擔部份手術費用。<br />\n李嘉誠指︰「醫療開支是重擔，中產家庭在面對危疾時，往往也感吃力，以至錯過治療的機會，基金會期望能幫上一把，助其減輕醫療開支，讓他們受惠先進科技的成果，獲得良好的生活質素。」<br />\n計劃自去年七月至今，已有10名病人受惠，他們獲得的資助金額共超過200萬元。養和醫院與李嘉誠基金會期望是次合作，可令更多有需要的病人得到適切治療。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190311/59356815\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190311%2F59356815&d=%2BklfNN7Cu7rnXjHLlXUq6K3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=799ce493\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190311%2F59356815&h=d5681e0b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190311/59356815</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"169aff5c37a13b77b525ecbb56a5083c7af31123","tid":1057001,"uid":31841,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:51:39.000Z","msg":"俾定自己醫療費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"074807e3a72d89665d731fc3c50a37a5e8fab526","tid":1057001,"uid":11127,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:52:19.000Z","msg":"捐十分一比我睇醫生ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9380773e6390812198778eb50349ac1b0a5b9e01","tid":1057001,"uid":69218,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:54:22.000Z","msg":"養撚埋班住半山嘅有錢佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c957e4f79041db26472779b18a37df23710dbd2","tid":1057001,"uid":76747,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:54:39.000Z","msg":"10幾萬, 哇屌<br />\n我都有心臟病快D資助我"},{"pid":"11829347d3084dd8d79340a35ff0e99739f1e779","tid":1057001,"uid":91693,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:55:58.000Z","msg":"首先你要有錢入養和"},{"pid":"079307f0383ddfe0018468bcdd80ac974deb5940","tid":1057001,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:57:14.000Z","msg":"講真養和入門口已經跳標"},{"pid":"88621b33afd8b72381e6ba8b082de710bee215be","tid":1057001,"uid":10692,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:57:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"56e8027b87fc243a189e6c067e84d37359b5958e","tid":1057001,"uid":58413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:57:54.000Z","msg":"點解唔俾瑪麗？"},{"pid":"3053647400263d474fe8f65c06b420aaac997fb8","tid":1057001,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11829347d3084dd8d79340a35ff0e99739f1e779","tid":1057001,"uid":91693,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:55:58.000Z","msg":"首先你要有錢入養和"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T15:00:02.000Z","msg":"claim保險咪入到囉"},{"pid":"3270f919279bcdb90d40a551846093d437cc4f3f","tid":1057001,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T15:05:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ChayJKS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FChayJKS.png&h=7965d558&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cf490a861cf4ce79d84f76ae49edd3d0c35c0476","tid":1057001,"uid":20317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,